    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to any variety of paper that has been processed to make it transparent; for use especially in tracing and in overlay. Types  include natural tracing, imitation parchment, and glassine papers. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
